后端配置说明文档（给后端开发人员）
问题背景
前端部署在 sz.scpaxy.cn，需要跨域请求后端 API bc.scpaxy.cn。当前 /stu/saveHcMark 接口报错：
java.lang.NullPointerException: Cannot read field "schoolCode" because "stu" is null
原因：跨子域名请求时，浏览器未携带 Session Cookie，导致后端无法识别用户身份。
需要的后端配置修改
1. Cookie 配置（关键）
登录成功后设置 Cookie 时，需要添加以下属性：
// Spring Boot 示例
Cookie cookie = new Cookie("JSESSIONID", session.getId());
cookie.setDomain(".scpaxy.cn");    // 允许所有子域名共享
cookie.setPath("/");                // 所有路径可用
cookie.setSecure(true);             // 仅 HTTPS 传输
cookie.setHttpOnly(true);           // 防止 XSS
// SameSite=None 需要通过 response header 设置
response.addCookie(cookie);
response.setHeader("Set-Cookie", 
    "JSESSIONID=" + session.getId() + 
    "; Domain=.scpaxy.cn" +
    "; Path=/" +
    "; SameSite=None" +
    "; Secure" +
    "; HttpOnly");
或使用 Spring Session 配置：
# application.yml
server:
  servlet:
    session:
      cookie:
        domain: .scpaxy.cn
        same-site: none
        secure: true
        http-only: true
2. CORS 配置
@Configuration
public class CorsConfig implements WebMvcConfigurer {
    
    @Override
    public void addCorsMappings(CorsRegistry registry) {
        registry.addMapping("/**")
            // 不能使用 *，必须指定具体域名
            .allowedOrigins(
                "https://sz.scpaxy.cn",
                "https://bc.scpaxy.cn"
            )
            .allowedMethods("GET", "POST", "PUT", "DELETE", "OPTIONS")
            .allowedHeaders("*")
            .allowCredentials(true)  // 关键：允许携带凭证
            .maxAge(3600);
    }
}
或使用 Filter 方式：
@Component
public class CorsFilter implements Filter {
    
    @Override
    public void doFilter(ServletRequest req, ServletResponse res, FilterChain chain)
            throws IOException, ServletException {
        
        HttpServletResponse response = (HttpServletResponse) res;
        HttpServletRequest request = (HttpServletRequest) req;
        
        String origin = request.getHeader("Origin");
        
        // 允许的域名列表
        List<String> allowedOrigins = Arrays.asList(
            "https://sz.scpaxy.cn",
            "https://bc.scpaxy.cn"
        );
        
        if (origin != null && allowedOrigins.contains(origin)) {
            response.setHeader("Access-Control-Allow-Origin", origin);
        }
        
        response.setHeader("Access-Control-Allow-Credentials", "true");
        response.setHeader("Access-Control-Allow-Methods", "GET, POST, PUT, DELETE, OPTIONS");
        response.setHeader("Access-Control-Allow-Headers", "Content-Type, Accept, X-Requested-With");
        response.setHeader("Access-Control-Max-Age", "3600");
        
        // 处理预检请求
        if ("OPTIONS".equalsIgnoreCase(request.getMethod())) {
            response.setStatus(HttpServletResponse.SC_OK);
            return;
        }
        
        chain.doFilter(req, res);
    }
}
3. 配置检查清单
配置项	需要的值	说明
Cookie Domain	.scpaxy.cn	注意前面的点，表示所有子域名
Cookie SameSite	None	允许跨站请求携带
Cookie Secure	true	SameSite=None 必须配合 HTTPS
CORS Allow-Origin	具体域名（不能是 *）	当 credentials=true 时必须
CORS Allow-Credentials	true	允许携带 Cookie
OPTIONS 预检	返回 200	浏览器会先发送预检请求
4. Nginx 配置（如果使用反向代理）
server {
    listen 443 ssl;
    server_name bc.scpaxy.cn;
    
    location / {
        proxy_pass http://backend-server;
        
        # 传递原始 Host
        proxy_set_header Host $host;
        proxy_set_header X-Real-IP $remote_addr;
        proxy_set_header X-Forwarded-For $proxy_add_x_forwarded_for;
        proxy_set_header X-Forwarded-Proto $scheme;
        
        # 关键：传递 Cookie
        proxy_set_header Cookie $http_cookie;
        proxy_pass_header Set-Cookie;
        
        # CORS headers（如果后端未配置）
        add_header Access-Control-Allow-Origin "https://sz.scpaxy.cn" always;
        add_header Access-Control-Allow-Credentials "true" always;
        add_header Access-Control-Allow-Methods "GET, POST, OPTIONS" always;
        add_header Access-Control-Allow-Headers "Content-Type, Accept" always;
        
        # 处理 OPTIONS 预检
        if ($request_method = OPTIONS) {
            return 204;
        }
    }
}
5. 验证步骤
配置完成后，请验证： 步骤 1：检查登录响应头
curl -I "https://bc.scpaxy.cn/stu/login?accountName=xxx&accountPass=xxx"
期望看到：
Set-Cookie: JSESSIONID=xxx; Domain=.scpaxy.cn; Path=/; SameSite=None; Secure; HttpOnly
Access-Control-Allow-Origin: https://sz.scpaxy.cn
Access-Control-Allow-Credentials: true
步骤 2：检查 OPTIONS 预检响应
curl -X OPTIONS -I "https://bc.scpaxy.cn/stu/saveHcMark" \
  -H "Origin: https://sz.scpaxy.cn" \
  -H "Access-Control-Request-Method: POST"
期望返回 200/204 和正确的 CORS 头。
